es.fnl.fsm
Class ExactScanner<E>

java.lang.Object
  es.fnl.fsm.ExactScanner<E>

public final class ExactScanner<E>
extends Object

This scanner implements sequence comparison over Iterators using the Knuth-Morris-Pratt pattern matching algorithm.

As this is an exact matcher, elements are compared using equals(Object). Note that the empty pattern is illegal, while a null in the pattern is allowed to match a null in the sequence if at the right position.

Author:
Florian Leitner
